    <div data-ref="Lee2015">Lee, A., Chan, S. K. & Fan, L. T. (2015). Stimulation of the wrist acupuncture point PC6 for preventing postoperative nausea and vomiting. Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews, (11), CD003281.</div>
  </template>
</FrameworkLayout>
